    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（mihoさんに病院まで乗せて行ってもらった後）\n（俺は風邪と診断され、静養するように言われてしまった）",
      "startTime": 3.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "まったく。たまたま車があったから良かったものの\n倒れるまで体調不良を放置なんて、社会人失格ですよ",
      "startTime": 13.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "他所では、マネージャーがアイドルを車で送迎するのに\n星見プロでは、アイドルがマネージャーを運ぶなんて",
      "startTime": 22.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ……貴方にとって運が良かったかは知りませんが\n私の運転で運ばれるなんて、お気の毒でしたね",
      "startTime": 31.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "い、いえ、そんなことは……\nmihoさんがいてくれて、助かりました",
      "startTime": 38,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、撮影までに完治させていただければ結構ですが\nでは、今日のところは失礼します",
      "startTime": 45.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――撮影当日",
      "startTime": 49.6000030518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（運転大丈夫かな……mihoさんのことだから）\n（きっと最後はなんとかしてくれると思うんだけど）",
      "startTime": 55.7333363851,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "目線はこっちで、ポーズは……こうでしょうか\nいい感じですか？　ふふ、ありがとうございます",
      "startTime": 66.7666694642,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "普段、車を運転するのか……？　ええ\nたまにレンタカーを借りて、走らせることはありますよ",
      "startTime": 76.7000027975,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "夜に誰もいない道を飛ばすのは、気分がいいですね\nこんな素敵な車なら、もっと気持ちいいんでしょうけど",
      "startTime": 85.1666694642,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（あはは……物は言いようだな……こういう時の）\n（mihoさんのそつのなさは、いっそすがすがしいよ）",
      "startTime": 93.6333361309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "この後の運転も、とても楽しみにしていたんです\n……一緒に免許を取った友人に、自慢したいと思います",
      "startTime": 102.5666694642,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "さあ、あとは運転シーンの撮影だけだが……\nどうか事故だけは起こりませんように……！",
      "startTime": 112.7333361309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "あのコーナーはスピードを落とさず……ダウンフォース\nを活かして、外側から飛び込んでさらに加速……",
      "startTime": 119.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "み、mihoさん、CMとは思えない狂気的な顔で\n車に乗り込んで行くぞ……大丈夫だろうか……",
      "startTime": 126.7333361309,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1166.6613261999998,
          "startTime": 124.0666694642
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_car-door-close-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4833.325195299992,
          "startTime": 127.7333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_car-04.m4a",
      "startTime": 131.4728198369
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "え！？　そんなエンジンを吹かして、一体どうする\nつもり……ほ、ホイルスピンしてるぞ！　凄い煙だ！",
      "startTime": 135.5000048321,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_car-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7903.0383110000175,
          "startTime": 140.1363818169
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_car-02.m4a",
          "delay": 16033.325958299996,
          "startTime": 148.2666694642
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_car-door-close-01.m4a",
          "delay": 17733.325958300014,
          "startTime": 149.9666694642
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "と思ったら、カーレーサー顔負けの加速ー！？\nエンジンがうなりを上げて、まるで地響きのようだ！",
      "startTime": 143.4333381654,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "そこからドリフトして……な、なんと一回転したー！\nmiho選手、煙を上げる車から颯爽と降りてきます！",
      "startTime": 151.2000027975,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 150.8333361309
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-mhk010.m4a",
      "text": "……どうでしたか？\nなかなか迫力のあるドリフトだったでしょう？",
      "startTime": 158.1333361309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-mhk011.m4a",
      "text": "車のメーカーの人達も見に来ているのに\nただスムーズに運転しても、つまらないですからね",
      "startTime": 164.1333361309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "かなりワイルドな運転で驚きました\nでもこの間まで、ひど……いえ個性的な運転だったのに",
      "startTime": 170.3666694642,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-mhk012.m4a",
      "text": "人に病院まで運ばせておいて、その言い草ですか\nまぁ、今回は極力、事前に準備はしておきましたので",
      "startTime": 180.4666694642,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7399.992624999982,
          "startTime": 183.3333361309
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　……これ、さっき走ってた道のマップですか？\nうわ、どう加速してブレーキ踏むか、全部書いてある",
      "startTime": 189.5333361309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-mhk013.m4a",
      "text": "ある日突然、運転がうまくなる訳もないですし\nとなればもう、丸暗記で対応するしかないですから",
      "startTime": 197.8666694642,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-mhk014.m4a",
      "text": "動画でレーサーの走りを研究して、夜な夜な試しました\nまぁ……このやり方でいくと決めたのは、つい最近です",
      "startTime": 207.2000027975,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-mhk015.m4a",
      "text": "どこかの誰かが、情けなくもぶっ倒れたおかげで\n初心者マークのまま、深夜に車を飛ばす羽目になって",
      "startTime": 216.9000027975,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
